    >>> with pa.input_stream('example.gz') as stream:
    ...     stream.read()
    ...
    b'some data'

    Create a readable PythonFile (NativeFile) from a a Python file object:

    >>> with open('example.txt', mode='w') as f:
    ...     f.write('some text')
    ...
    9
